When the network is unavailable, you can try the following methods:
 1.Try replacing your phone card. It could be a drain.
 2.Try to turn on the wifi hotspot on your phone. Click the system Settings button below to turn on the wifi hotspot in the android system Settings and then go back to the vending machine Settings screen to find fault diagnosis => network test.
 3.Try to check whether the network antenna of the machine is plugged in properly and whether the antenna is placed outside the machine (if the antenna is placed inside the housing, the network will be affected and the machine will often be disconnected).
 The machine is still offline after the above test, please contact the customer service.

manual：
 1，The gray button is not clickable, and the blue button is clickable
 2，The app has been downloaded. Click Install to install the new version of APP. Click Delete to delete the apk file.
 3，The app is installed, click the uninstall button to uninstall the app
 4，Click to check the update button or download address button, you can get the latest version of the app download address. After you get the download address, you can click the download button.
 5，Click the download button to download the app.After the download is complete, you can install it.
 Note: Downloading and upgrading will consume a lot of traffic. The APP is best downloaded from a PC and copied to a U disk to install and upgrade.
